{
  "stem": "24830.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my brother will sleep half of the night and I will stay up listening.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then my brother-- I will wake up my brother, and he will stay, and I will sleep.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we did this for-- for few night.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Then my mother say-- she got so worried that she decided to send us to Free France.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So the-- she sent us to the woman in charge of the-- you know, the worker.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She live in the banlieue outside of Paris.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she send my brother and I there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And from there, she pay somebody to take us from Ocuppy France-- it's called Occupy France to Free France, [FRENCH].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I remember we went to the station.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I remember, it was really-- I never forgot, because when I-- it was very-- the worst place to be is the station.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That's where the German-- because of course, everybody want to escape.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "That's where they pick.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So I didn't take my Jewish card.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I took my student card with me, you know, like a student.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then we went in the station.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And inside the station, there was a-- like a school bus, a big bus.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And all inside were a lot of-- full of people with sad eyes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And then I understood, they were arrested.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I look at it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I say, I should be with them, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It was a very, very sad feeling.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when we got to the town, where we supposed to pass from-- I forget.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wrote it down.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I [INAUDIBLE] the name of the-- and the man, who supposed to take care of us, say, well, I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But you cannot pass in a boat, because the German kill people yesterday, who were-- and it's too dangerous.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
